'''Sanskrit''' ([[devanagari]]: संस्कृता वाच्, IAST. saṃskṛtā vāk, «literaturine kel'») — [[Indii|Indijan]] amuine kirjankel' koverikahan sintetižen grammatikanke, üks' sen oficialižiš kelišpäi. «Sanskrit»-sana üksnäze znamoičeb «ümbriratud, vigatoi»<ref>Кочергина В. А. Санскрит. — М.: Академический проект, 2007. — lp. 3. ISBN 978-5-8291-0851-9. {{ref-ru}}</ref>. Aigaližiden kirjmuštnikoiden igä om läz 3,5 tuhad vot (kesk II voz'tuhad edel meiden erad).

Pagižijoiden lugu — 14 000 ristitud ([[2001]]).<ref name="Census">[http://censusindia.gov.in/Census_Data_2001/Census_Data_Online/Language/Statement5.htm Comparative speaker's strength of scheduled languages − 1971, 1981, 1991 and 2001 // Census of India (''censusindia.gov.in''), Office of the Registrar and Census Commissioner, 2001.] {{ref-en}}</ref>

